This project is a Machine Learning model that predicts whether a company will go bankrupt based on financial data.

The dataset contains financial information about Taiwanese companies and a target column called **bankrupt**:
- 0 â†’ Company is not bankrupt
- 1 â†’ Company is bankrupt

This project demonstrates a complete ML workflow from data loading to model deployment.

